query {
  ~version: 
}

docs {
  ## Get Running Code by ID
  ดึงข้อมูลรหัสเลขที่เอกสารอัตโนมัติเดียวตาม ID สำหรับสร้างรหัสเอกสาร (เช่น PR-001, PO-001)

  Retrieves a specific auto-numbering rule configuration used to generate sequential document codes.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Running code ID |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  > Permission key not found in seed; review needed.

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "type": "purchase_request",
      "config": {
        "A": "PR",
        "B": "YYYY",
        "C": "MM",
        "D": "0001",
        "format": "{A}{B}{C}{D}"
      },
      "created_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 404 | Running code not found |
}

